try","category-wisdom-al-hikmah","tag-agreed-upon-muttafaqun-alayhi","tag-lawful-halal","tag-manners-adab","tag-mosques-masjid","tag-sitting-al-maqad","tag-sleep-al-nawm"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3Z4","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":3042,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/24\/pilgrims-makkah-madinah-quds\/","url_meta":{"origin":15318,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Pilgrimage: No religious travel but to Mecca, Medina, Jerusalem","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not undertake a religious journey but to three mosques: the Sacred Mosque in Mecca, the Mosque of the Messenger of Allah, and the Furthest Mosque in Jerusalem.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1189, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1397 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25822,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/28\/allah-in-front-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":15318,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Allah in front of you when praying","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 28, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf one of you is in prayer, let him not spit in front of himself, for Allah is in front of him as he prays.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 398, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 547 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17034,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/reminded-me-of-ayat\/","url_meta":{"origin":15318,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Allah have mercy on one who reminded me","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was listening to a man recite the Quran in the mosque and he said, \u201cMay Allah have mercy upon him. He reminded me of a verse I was made to forget.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5038, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 788 Grade: Muttafaqun\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31753,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/two-rakaat-after-travel\/","url_meta":{"origin":15318,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Praying two cycles upon return from a journey","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, returned home in the forenoon after a journey, he would enter the mosque and pray two cycles before sitting down. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2922, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 716 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14956,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/14\/last-ten-nights-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":15318,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadr in last ten nights of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSearch for the Night of Decree in the odd nights among the last ten nights of Ramadan.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2017, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1169 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13557,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/13\/tahiyyat-al-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":15318,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Greet mosque with Tahiyyatul Masjid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you enters the mosque, let him pray two cycles before he sits down.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 444, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 714 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15318","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15318"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15318\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15318"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=15318"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=15318"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}